## Instructions

Create a complete entity page for "{{ entityName }}". Follow the entity page specification:

1. **YAML frontmatter:** Use id: entity.{{ slug }}, set title to the entity name, status: review (new page, not yet reviewed), confidence as average of claim confidences, today's date ({{ today }}) for created and updated. Include relevant lowercase tags.

2. **Body:** Write a concise encyclopedia-style description (2-3 paragraphs). Weave in the description and source context naturally.

